"ğŸ„editconf"
"â˜„ï¸alacritty"
"ğŸ¦”xmonad"
"ğŸ§Šxinitrc"
"ğŸ¢setup_arch"
"ğŸ©polybar"
"ğŸ“’reading-list"
"ğŸ“bookmark"
"ğŸ””notify"
"ğŸƒntu_course_bookmark"
"ğŸ§°other"
